aea game has arrived, dood!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1233880/extras/3e7da0de832521dde45769c0284b32de.poster.avif?t=1732584341\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1233880/extras/3e7da0de832521dde45769c0284b32de.webm?t=1732584341\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1233880/extras/3e7da0de832521dde45769c0284b32de.mp4?t=1732584341\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
